pageContext.title: U.S. East Coast Rollout
pageContext.description: MITH is pleased to announce that it will be hosting the U.S. East Coast Open Annotation Data Model Rollout on **Monday, May 6**. This meeting is free, but registration is required due to space limitations. Lunch will be provided. Visit [the rollout page](http://www.openannotation.org/RolloutInfo.html) for more information, including [an agenda](http://www.openannotation.org/MITH_Agenda.html) and [registration](https://www.eventville.com/Catalog/EventRegistration1.asp?Eventid=1010271). **Please register by April 19**.
